</div><div class="module mod-sidebar    ">

		
	<div class="box-1 deepest">
	
				<h3 class="header"><span class="header-2"><span class="header-3">中央民族乐团介绍</span></span></h3>
				
		<div class="custom">
	<p>
	<a href="10-about-us/45" style="text-decoration: none;">中央民族乐团是当今我国最具民族代表性、最完整的国家民族乐团。乐团由庞大的民族管弦乐队和民族合唱队组成&hellip;&hellip;</a></p>
</div>		
	</div>
		
</div><div class="module mod-sidebar    ">

		
	<div class="box-1 deepest">
	
				
		<div class="custom">
	<h4>
	中国民族乐团合唱队</h4>
<p>
	<a href="10-about-us/47" style="text-decoration: none;">中央民族乐团合唱队是我国唯一一支具有浓郁民族风格的国家级民族声乐合唱队，以演唱中国民间特色歌曲及各地区民歌改编的声乐作品见长&hellip;&hellip;</a></p>
</div>		
	</div>
		
</div><div class="module mod-sidebar    ">

		
	<div class="box-1 deepest">
	
				
		<div class="custom">
	<h4>
	中央民族乐团管弦乐队</h4>
<p>
	<a href="10-about-us/46" style="text-decoration: none;">中央民族乐团管弦乐队是我国民族音乐舞台上最具影响力的民族管弦乐队，舞台经验丰富，音乐风格多样&hellip;&hellip;</a></p>
</div>		
	</div>
		
</div><div class="module mod-sidebar    ">

		
	<div class="box-1 deepest">
	
				<h3 class="header"><span class="header-2"><span class="header-3">团长致辞</span></span></h3>
				
		<div class="custom">
	<p>
	<a href="10-about-us/7" style="text-decoration: none;">当人们听到远处轻舟荡漾、春风吹拂、江水涟漪的琵琶与琴曲时，《春江花月夜》的优美与秀丽，《二泉映月》的哀怨与刚毅&hellip;&hellip;</a></p>
</div>		
	</div>
		
</div><div class="module mod-sidebar    last">

		
	<div class="box-1 deepest">
	
				<h3 class="header"><span class="header-2"><span class="header-3">地址</span></span></h3>
				
		<div class="custom">
	<p><span style="font-size: small;">北京市朝阳区北四环小营路15号<br /></span>No.15 Xiaoying Road, North 4th Ring,<br />Chaoyang District, Beijing, China<br /><span style="font-size: small;">中央民族乐团  <span style="color: #ffcc00;">(</span><span style="color: #ffcc00; font-size: small;"><a href="http://map.baidu.com/?newmap=1&amp;l=18&amp;tn=B_NORMAL_MAP&amp;c=12960994,4837882&amp;cc=bj&amp;s=s%26wd%3D%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E4%B9%90%E5%9B%A2%26c%3D131%26src%3D0%26wd2%3D%26sug%3D0%26l%3D12%26from%3Dwebmap&amp;sc=0">查看位置</a><strong>)<br /></strong></span></span>Chinese National Orchestra  <a href="http://j.map.baidu.com/9JqZg"><span style="color: #ffcc00;">(map)</span><br /></a><span style="font-size: small;">邮编：100101 </span><br />〒100101</p></div>		
